oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Shady Grove Baptist Church
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Shady Grove Missionary Baptist Church, Northshore Drive, Knox County, TN. It was organized in 1837 and was one of the oldest churches in East Tennessee. Sign on door has dates 1837 and 1935.
